{
  "texts": [
    "As expected, we observed less misclassification than correct classification.",
    "Internal content was not significantly misclassified as external content (Fig. 3c, r =.08, p = 0.32), and external content was not significantly misclassified as internal content (Fig.",
    "3d, r =.06, p = 0.503).",
    "To summarize, we found greater correct classification of internal content than misclassification (R 2 = 0.44 vs. R 2 = 0.01).",
    "We also found greater correct classification of external content than misclassification (R 2 = 0.11 vs. R 2 = 0.00)."
  ]
}